clientside.managers

Class ClientManagement

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientside.managers.ClientManagement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class ClientManagement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.beans.PropertyChangeListener
    Class description: Manager for the client side of the game. Runs Tic Tac Toe and manages the socket of the client. This class observes the object input stream of the socket.
    Version:
    September 24, 2019
    Author:
    Holly Harnack (806547)

        void moved(int moveLocation)

        Parameters:
        moveLocation - - Integer value given by the button that the client clicked, tracking location of client move.

      • checkTie
